WEBVTT

00:00:01.429 --> 00:00:04.860
mir hobn geendikt vegn dem

00:00:04.860 --> 00:00:08.370
ven ir hot genumen di tsvey yinglekh, di tsvey,

00:00:07.403 --> 00:00:08.308
shtubn-dinstn.

00:00:08.370 --> 00:00:12.814
shtubn-dinstn, un ir hot zey tseshlogn.

00:00:12.313 --> 00:00:14.872
YES. befor zey hobn gevolt hargenen mayn bruder.

00:00:16.093 --> 00:00:20.778
nu, iz gegangen un m'hot mikh gerufn tsu dem tsum blok-ALTESTER,

00:00:21.122 --> 00:00:22.854
un er hot tsu mir gezogt,

00:00:23.113 --> 00:00:28.350
"yetst geystu MAL tsu der arbet, un ven du kumst MAL tsurik, geystu MAL

00:00:28.350 --> 00:00:31.750
tsum hengen." vayl m'hot yedn gehongen ven m'iz tsurikgekumen oykhet.

00:00:31.750 --> 00:00:33.553
yedn tog m'iz tsurikgekumen hot men gehongen.

00:00:34.622 --> 00:00:36.357
un mayn bruder hot genumen veynen

00:00:36.357 --> 00:00:40.117
vos ikh hob dos getun. zogt er, veyst nisht vos hot oyf dir gevart. un meshiekh hostu nisht derlebt.

00:00:40.647 --> 00:00:43.307
un ikh hob dikh opgeratevet dem lebn, un vos vet zayn yetst mit dir?

00:00:43.380 --> 00:00:44.977
zog ikh, hob nisht keyn moyre far mir.

00:00:45.051 --> 00:00:49.719
un er hot mir gezogt mir, der UNK er hot mir gezogt mir az far nakht vet er mikh aroysfirn tsum hengen,

00:00:50.147 --> 00:00:53.060
bin ikh aroysgegangen shoyn tsum apel shoyn tsedreyt.

00:00:53.185 --> 00:00:57.299
un der der S.S. iz dokh mit undz geven tsuzamen.

00:00:57.299 --> 00:00:59.085
er hot dokh undz opgefirt tsu der arbet.

00:00:59.698 --> 00:01:02.510
zogt er, "vos bistu MAL RUNTER azoy, nisht gut GESCHLAFEN?"

00:01:03.462 --> 00:01:04.974
ikh zog, "ikh hob PROBLEMS.

00:01:05.453 --> 00:01:08.991
mayn blok ALTESTER vil mikh haynt firn tsum hengen." zogt er, "WHAT?

00:01:09.182 --> 00:01:10.695
WAS hostu mit im gemakht?"

00:01:11.241 --> 00:01:15.808
zog ikh, "s'gekumen mayn bruder, un ikh hob im arayngenumen in blok arayn tsu shlofn mit mir,

00:01:17.653 --> 00:01:19.891
un zey hobn gevolt im TOTES SCHLAGEN.

00:01:19.999 --> 00:01:25.291
ikh veys dokh shoyn WAS UNK makhn EVERY MORNING, dan HAB ikh zey ZERSCHLAGEN."

00:01:25.332 --> 00:01:26.929
zogt er, "gut hostu gemakht!

00:01:27.103 --> 00:01:31.822
gut hostu gemakht." "JA gut, ober der der blok eltster vil mikh derfar hengen!"

00:01:32.031 --> 00:01:34.488
"ICH gey mit dir tsu ha- ICH gey mit dir tsu im."

00:01:34.647 --> 00:01:37.594
er geyt mit mir tsu im. nokh der arbet vet er mikh opfirn.

00:01:38.781 --> 00:01:43.382
un nokh der arbet, m'geyt aheym, geyt er mit mir tsum blok ALTESTER un geyt arayn in OFFICE arayn,

00:01:44.974 --> 00:01:48.579
zogt er, vu zenen di tsvey shtubn-dinstn? geyt der blok ALTESTER un get aruf.!

00:01:48.687 --> 00:01:52.866
un di tsvey shtubn-dinstn gebn a kum arayn, zey hobn gezen dem S.S. man mit mir,

00:01:52.888 --> 00:01:55.447
hobn zikh derfreyt az m'geyt mikh firn tsum hengen.

00:01:55.858 --> 00:01:58.940
der S.S. zogt, "WHAT'S HAPPENED?" "er hot undz GESCHLAGEN."

00:01:59.790 --> 00:02:04.639
zogt er, yetst zogt er, eb ikh aykh gebn. hot er zey tsugegebn nokh k- tsvey knakers tsu dem un dem,

00:02:04.639 --> 00:02:07.429
un zogt er, "zolst MAL nisht ANFANGEN mit dem yunger!"

00:02:06.962 --> 00:02:10.078
un di shtubn-dinstn zenen gevezn ver? yidn tsi?

00:02:09.645 --> 00:02:10.567
yidn.

00:02:11.164 --> 00:02:14.364
un nisht onfangen nokh a mol mit dem mentsh, mit dem BOY.

00:02:14.590 --> 00:02:19.680
un nokh dem zogt er zogt er tsum blok ALTESTER, ikh hob dir gezogt zolst mer akhtung gebn oyf dem oyf dem BOY.

00:02:19.787 --> 00:02:22.008
zolst mer nisht TOUCHn dem BOY!

00:02:22.487 --> 00:02:26.345
zogt er, JAWOHL, un er hot geshrign JAWOHL. ikh vel mer shoyn mer nisht redn.

00:02:27.499 --> 00:02:29.889
un der un der S.S. man iz avek.

00:02:30.908 --> 00:02:39.356
S.S. man iz avek. un ikh gey aroys, mayn bruder shtarbt, er vil mikh shoyn zen. geb ikh a kum arayn tsurik in blok arayn, er veynt, er kumt arayn, zogt er, "nu, abi ikh ze dikh nokh!"

00:02:40.847 --> 00:02:47.945
un ikh zits azoy, un m'redt azoy un m'redt azoy, git der blok ALTESTER a kum arayn, un geyt tsu glaykh tsu mir, un zogt er tsu mir, "kum arayn tsu mir in OFFICE arayn."

00:02:48.323 --> 00:02:55.455
gey ikh arayn tsu im in OFFICE arayn. "far vos hostu mir nisht dertseylt host aza min," zogt er, "vos iz dayns a FAMILY der S.S. man? der vos vos iz er dayns?"

00:02:55.512 --> 00:02:57.784
zog ikh, "er iz mayns azoy gut vi dayns.

00:02:58.718 --> 00:03:05.614
vos iz vikhtik?" zogt er, "er halt fun dir azoy? un ikh zol dir nisht a-" zogt er, "vey, ikh hob far im moyre." zog ikh, "muzt tun vos er zogt dir."

00:03:07.527 --> 00:03:15.368
zogt er, "yetst fun haynt op, yede nakht ven du vest aheymkumen, zolstu nisht shteyn in der LINE nokh a zup, zolst araynkumen tsu mir in OFFICE arayn, mir veln esn tsuzamen nakht mol."

00:03:15.694 --> 00:03:19.789
zog ikh, "ikh hob a bruder. ikh vil esn mit im tsuzamen."

00:03:19.963 --> 00:03:21.914
zogt er, "vestu brengen dem bruder oykhet."

00:03:23.440 --> 00:03:27.804
hob ikh ongehoybn tsu brengen dem bruder. m'hot gegesn dort nakht mol. dort hot men gekent esn vifl m'vil.

00:03:27.557 --> 00:03:28.968
avu, tsu dem kapo?

00:03:29.565 --> 00:03:32.900
nisht der nisht di, dos iz der blok ALTE- der firer fun dem blok.

00:03:31.675 --> 00:03:32.799
fun dem blok.

00:03:32.940 --> 00:03:38.131
dos iz geven der firer fun dem blok. un er hot mikh arayngefirt ikh zol esn mit im tsuzamen, mitn bruder tsuzamen.

00:03:39.184 --> 00:03:41.861
shoyn. dos iz eyn mol avek.

00:03:41.867 --> 00:03:48.695
vos iz vayter hot zikh gevezn vayter mit dem brilantn vos ikh hob gebrengt di brilantn aheym un m'hot dos bahaltn,

00:03:48.972 --> 00:03:52.003
s'hot zikh geendikt der fir un fertsikster yor,

00:03:52.566 --> 00:03:59.557
dos iz gevezn in JANUARY der EIGHTEEN, dos iz geven farn EIGHTEEN.

00:03:59.557 --> 00:04:02.803
SLICHA, dos iz geven a zekhtsn- in zekhtstn JANUARY.

00:04:03.163 --> 00:04:08.450
hot men oysgeklibn ale yugntlekhe, finef hundert yunge boyes,

00:04:08.450 --> 00:04:14.025
hot men undz gegebn a loz arayn in a blok arayn, un m'hot gezogt dos geyt oyf kastrirn.

00:04:15.043 --> 00:04:17.349
haynt bay nakht geyt men undz kastrirn.

00:04:19.363 --> 00:04:20.892
vifl zent ir gevezn?

00:04:19.380 --> 00:04:24.321
finef hundert. finef hundert boyes.

00:04:24.321 --> 00:04:30.056
dos iz geven JANUARY finef un fertsik, JANUARY finef un fertsik, m'geyt kastrirn.

00:04:29.691 --> 00:04:30.799
ale yidn?

00:04:30.552 --> 00:04:31.626
alts yidn.

00:04:33.893 --> 00:04:41.835
shoyn, ikh hob nisht gevust. Khaim Ernberg hot shoyn gevust vu m'geyt undz firn, vos vos vart oyf undz. er hot shoyn gevust in droysn vos m'geyt tun mit undz.

00:04:42.415 --> 00:04:48.028
hot er zikh ongehoybn zikh, ir hert, un er iz gegangen arayn tsu dem blok ALTESTER vos hot undz gehitn,

00:04:49.485 --> 00:04:53.748
un redt mit im. zogt er, ken ikh, zogt er, aroysnemen, zogt er, a yunger fun danet?

00:04:54.362 --> 00:04:58.085
oyb ikh vel dir gebn dos vos dos tayerste in der velt iz.

00:04:58.767 --> 00:05:03.792
zogt er, "vos iz dos tayerste? vos kenstu mir gebn? broyt? esn? trinken?" zogt er, "neyn.

00:05:03.792 --> 00:05:05.308
nokh tayers."

00:05:05.550 --> 00:05:07.007
"gelt? gold?"

00:05:07.007 --> 00:05:08.126
"brilantn."

00:05:08.267 --> 00:05:10.690
zogt er, "brilantn? du host brilantn?"

00:05:11.625 --> 00:05:16.023
"oyb du vest tsuzogn, gebn dos vort, du zolt aroys dem BOY, breng ikh dir groyse brilantn."

00:05:17.548 --> 00:05:22.790
ver iz der BOY? s'a BOY, zogt er, mayns a shteterisher. ikh vil er zol zayn mit mir tsuzamen.

00:05:24.720 --> 00:05:29.118
un vos vet dir zayn UNK vest hobn fir NINETY NINE, tsi du host finef? eyner veyniker.

00:05:31.048 --> 00:05:39.108
zogt er tsun im, "oyb du vest haltn dos moyl, vel ikh mir du makhn dos BUSINESS, nor du muzt onzogn dem BOY er zol nisht dervegn tsu dertseyln er iz geven in dem blok."

00:05:39.368 --> 00:05:42.788
zogt er, fun dem vet zayn hundert protsent. keyner vet nisht visn.

00:05:43.182 --> 00:05:47.867
un er iz avekgelofn, un er hot im gebrengt im dray shteyner, yeder shteyn iz shoyn finef karat tsen karat.

00:05:47.873 --> 00:05:50.257
un er hot im gegebn a leyg avek oyfn tish, "ze vos do tut zikh!

00:05:50.257 --> 00:05:52.355
vest mir gebn di hant? tsvishn undz."

00:05:52.665 --> 00:06:00.219
zogt er, vi iz zayn numer? nayntsn tsvey fir un draysik. geyt arayn in blok, get er a kum arayn, zogt er, "nayntsn tsvey fir un DREISSIG KAMME DOCH MAL aher!"

00:06:01.103 --> 00:06:07.276
un shrayt tsvey dray mol. zog ikh, a brokh tsu mayne yorn. ikh veys dokh gornisht vos Khaim hot in droysn getun, vos er hot far mir gemakht.

00:06:07.276 --> 00:06:10.243
un shrayt mikh. zog ikh, "ikh bin shoyn der ershter?"

00:06:10.553 --> 00:06:14.006
un gey ahin tsun im, un firt mikh arayn in OFFICE arayn, ze ikh Khaim Ernberg.

00:06:14.451 --> 00:06:18.342
zogt er shtil, "baruik dikh. vest geyn mit mir aroys."

00:06:19.851 --> 00:06:25.245
un zogt mir on der blok ALTESTER, zolst gedenken, zolst MAL di shnal tsuhaltn, ven nisht, zogt er, knal ICH DICH.

00:06:25.555 --> 00:06:28.181
nisht nisht redn keyn vort az du bist do gevezn.

00:06:28.339 --> 00:06:31.438
un ikh mit im aroys un ikh bin gegangen tsurik tsu der arbet.

00:06:31.495 --> 00:06:34.627
vos veyst yener vu ikh bin geven? bay a dokter, bay shmo- UNK.

00:06:34.971 --> 00:06:36.433
un gegangen tsurik tsu der arbet.

00:06:36.861 --> 00:06:41.039
in aza monat hot er mikh opgeratevet fun eyns.

00:06:41.400 --> 00:06:49.286
in akhtstn yanuar, hot men oysgeklibn oyf aroystsugeyn oyfn toytn-marsh.

00:06:49.286 --> 00:06:52.886
got zol danken ikh bin shoyn do oyf dem oykhet. ikh mitn bruder.

00:06:52.892 --> 00:06:56.311
ir veyst vos iz geshen tsu di andere vos m'hot

00:06:56.318 --> 00:06:59.180
di finef hundert vos m'hot arayngenumen tsu kastrirn?

00:06:58.073 --> 00:06:59.990
m'hot m'hot zey m'hot zey kastrirt.

00:06:59.963 --> 00:07:03.129
ir hot getrofn e- etlekhe nokh dem?

00:07:01.077 --> 00:07:06.962
ikh hob getrofn ey- ikh hob getrofn nokh dem nokh der milkhome in Yisroel, hob ikh getrofn, ikh hob gevoynt in Rekhovot,

00:07:07.086 --> 00:07:13.999
hob ikh getrofn a BOY fun Rishon Letsion, vos er hot gearbet in Rekhovot epes tsufelik,

00:07:14.121 --> 00:07:17.096
Yakobzon, heyst er. hot men zikh tsuzamen getrofn,

00:07:17.096 --> 00:07:21.506
un er iz geven tsuzamen mit mir in dem blok tsu shoyn kastrirn. er iz kastrirt.

00:07:22.204 --> 00:07:23.852
ale zenen gegangen kastrirn, bay nakht.

00:07:24.212 --> 00:07:27.344
vifl fun di vos m'hot kastrirt zenen geblibn lebn?

00:07:27.638 --> 00:07:31.428
ikh hob zikh, er er veyst nisht. ikh hob nor getrofn im.

00:07:32.262 --> 00:07:35.057
er veyst oykh nisht vifl. alts iz geven tsefayert.

00:07:35.181 --> 00:07:37.160
tsi m'hot geharget un geshosn, m'hot avekgeshikt,

00:07:37.160 --> 00:07:39.799
ikh bin gegangen nakher avek oyfn toytn-marsh,

00:07:39.805 --> 00:07:44.574
der toyter marsh iz gevezn, m'iz aroysgegangen a por,

00:07:43.483 --> 00:07:46.565
ober far far dem toytn-marsh m'hot aykh genumen,

00:07:46.403 --> 00:07:47.156
ya.

00:07:46.656 --> 00:07:50.160
in lager, m'hot aykh gegebn a n- a a numer?

00:07:49.913 --> 00:07:50.784
ya.

00:07:50.925 --> 00:07:55.160
zikher, azoy vi ikh bin ongekumen in Oyshvits, ikh bin geshtanen in LINE, ikh unter mayn bruder,

00:07:55.197 --> 00:07:56.987
un mayn NUMBER iz

00:07:55.515 --> 00:07:57.078
vos iz ayer numer?

00:07:56.987 --> 00:07:59.444
mayn NUMBER iz nayntsn tsvey fir un draysik.

00:08:01.776 --> 00:08:03.778
un in vos a blok zent ir gevezn?

00:08:03.970 --> 00:08:07.896
in blok fertsn. in Birkenau.

00:08:09.505 --> 00:08:14.611
di frage vos ir efsher hot aleyn geklert vegn dem,

00:08:14.938 --> 00:08:18.172
far vos iz der daytsher UNK gevorn azoy gut tsu aykh?

00:08:18.043 --> 00:08:18.766
o!

00:08:18.766 --> 00:08:25.828
ikh hob im gefregt a por mol, zog ikh, geb a kuk, ven ikh bin geven shoyn gut mit im bafrayndet, er hot mikh gegebn esn, trinken, ales, er hot mikh opgehitn,

00:08:25.828 --> 00:08:29.479
zog ikh, zog mir eyn zakh. hob ikh tsu im geredt azoy vi ikh red tsu aykh.

00:08:29.670 --> 00:08:34.052
vos hostu in mir gezen vos du bahandlst mikh azoy gut,

00:08:34.058 --> 00:08:36.819
un andere yidn, zog ikh, hargestu tsum toyt?

00:08:37.129 --> 00:08:41.543
shikst avek in gaz-kamern arayn, du tust ale tsores vos oyf der velt iz do.

00:08:42.342 --> 00:08:47.214
zogt er, "ICH vel dir MAL ZAGEN. ven ikh ze DICH, ze ICH mayn SON.

00:08:48.165 --> 00:08:52.530
ikh kuk oyf dir, ze ikh mayn SON. un dos vos ikh tu far dir."

00:08:56.451 --> 00:09:01.237
ikh bin avekgegangen nakher tsum marsh, oyfn toytn-marsh,

00:09:01.092 --> 00:09:02.993
un nokh a zakh farn marsh nokh.

00:09:02.610 --> 00:09:03.566
YES.

00:09:03.150 --> 00:09:10.150
s'iz epes nokh epes pasirt in AUSCHWITZ in der tsayt vos ir zent gevezn dortn, epes a farshidene,

00:09:09.850 --> 00:09:14.805
s'forge- ya, s'forgekumen in zumer nayntsn fir un fertsik iz forgekumen an oyfshtand.

00:09:10.150 --> 00:09:11.598
gesheenishn?

00:09:15.165 --> 00:09:19.344
hot di sirene ongehoybn tsu fayfn in gants Oyshvits hot ongehoybn tsu fayfn di sirene.

00:09:19.553 --> 00:09:24.339
un mir hobn nisht gevust vos do geyt tsu. di S.S. zenen aroys di ale, m'hot undz geheysn aropleygn oyf der erd.

00:09:24.480 --> 00:09:27.494
un zey hobn oyf undz getretn. gehaltn di fis oyf undz.

00:09:27.417 --> 00:09:28.997
avu zent ir geven demolts?

00:09:28.497 --> 00:09:29.649
bay der arbet.

00:09:29.649 --> 00:09:35.341
oyf yeder plats oyf der arbet vu m'hot gearbet zenen di S.S. gevezn, m'hot undz gehitn, s'gevezn m'hot undz gehitn.

00:09:34.842 --> 00:09:36.135
oysern lager?

00:09:36.242 --> 00:09:42.648
oysern lager. in a BUILDING. hot men undz gehitn, hot men tsuzamen genumen ale, avekgeleygt oyf der erd un oyf undz getretn.

00:09:42.688 --> 00:09:47.121
m'zol nisht oyfheybn keyn kop afile vos tut zikh. nakher s'hot zikh geendikt,

00:09:47.447 --> 00:09:52.419
hot es di di si- sirene az s'nokh alem, hobn zey undz opgelozt un m'zol tsurikgeyn tsu der arbet.

00:09:52.577 --> 00:09:56.923
nakher hot men gevoyer gevorn s'geven an oyfshtand, m'hot geshosn azoy fil un azoy fil un geharget azoy fil un azoy fil,

00:09:56.923 --> 00:10:00.824
un di di farvundete gebrengt in a in gaz-kamer arayn. m'hot oysgeharget.

00:10:00.863 --> 00:10:04.468
ir veyst eyntslheytn fun dem oyfshtand, tsi neyn?

00:10:04.187 --> 00:10:06.847
avade. vos?

00:10:06.938 --> 00:10:09.311
eyntslheytn vos,

00:10:08.153 --> 00:10:13.850
eyntslheytn, keyn sakh eyntslheytn veys ikh nisht. ikh veys az m'hot ales oysgeshosn, zey hobn nisht gekent gornisht oyftun.

00:10:14.042 --> 00:10:17.372
ir muzt farshteyn in Oyshvits yeder por meter iz gevezn a vakh in der heykh.

00:10:17.372 --> 00:10:20.089
un tsu di drotn tsutsugeyn ze'mir geven lektirizirt.

00:10:20.089 --> 00:10:27.064
un vi azoy zey hobn geharget, iz efsher hobn zey gehat a bisl gever, hot men geharget a por daytshn azoy eynem nokhn andern, ober m'hot di ale gekhapt.

00:10:27.610 --> 00:10:32.413
keyn shum plats iz nisht geven ofn oyftsuraysn m'zol kenen aroysloyfn.

00:10:33.600 --> 00:10:35.838
un m'hot aykh tsurikgefirt in lager arayn?

00:10:35.389 --> 00:10:36.142
ya.

00:10:36.705 --> 00:10:39.528
un ven ayer bruder iz ongekumen keyn AUSCHWITZ,

00:10:39.068 --> 00:10:39.990
ya.

00:10:39.528 --> 00:10:41.407
veyst ir fun vanet er iz gekumen?

00:10:41.042 --> 00:10:45.052
neyn, ikh veys nisht. er iz geven in farshidene lagern. in farshidene lagern iz er gevezn.

00:10:45.193 --> 00:10:48.123
un fun ayer familye hot er epes gehert in der tsayt?

00:10:47.522 --> 00:10:52.185
garnisht gornisht. nor vos iz, ven er iz ongekumen keyn Oyshvits, hot er mir hersht dertseylt mir

00:10:52.185 --> 00:10:55.532
vos iz gev- vos iz gevorn vos iz gevorn mit mayn foter.

00:10:56.044 --> 00:11:00.746
far vos? demolts ven ikh bin a- ikh bin avek foyer, far im,

00:11:01.140 --> 00:11:05.538
ikh bin dokh avek far im, ober vos er iz geblibn nokh biz mayn foter, biz biz tsu der WYSIEDLENIE.

00:11:05.747 --> 00:11:11.549
hot men nokh im aroysgenumen er zol oyfroymen di toyte, ir farshteyt, s'geven a sakh toyte gehargete, m'darf men oyfroymen,

00:11:11.549 --> 00:11:15.577
un dos oyfroymen. hot men aroysgenumen a finef un tsvontsik yinglekh. er iz geven tsvishn zey.

00:11:15.646 --> 00:11:18.590
ven m'hot mayn tatn geshosn, hot er mayn tate koyver geven oykhet.

00:11:18.590 --> 00:11:21.576
di ale yinglekh vos zenen geblibn oyftsuroymen di toyte,

00:11:21.576 --> 00:11:25.754
hobn oyfgeroymt mayn foter oykhet. hot er mir dertseylt az m'hot dem tatn geshosn.

00:11:26.537 --> 00:11:30.918
fun danet veys ikh di yedie fun im, vos er hot mir dertseylt mir un er hot im koyver gevezn.

00:11:30.942 --> 00:11:33.062
oyfn yidishn bes-oylem in Apt.

00:11:32.967 --> 00:11:33.737
in Apt.

00:11:33.473 --> 00:11:34.226
ya.

00:11:34.570 --> 00:11:39.154
un in lager, in AUSCHWITZ aleyn, ver zenen geven di onfirer? ir veyst zeyere nemener?

00:11:39.700 --> 00:11:40.487
d- NO.

00:11:41.725 --> 00:11:42.917
di vekhter?

00:11:44.020 --> 00:11:50.572
keyn nemen keyn nemen, ikh hob zey nor gekent, nor eyn zakh, ikh hob nor gekent oyfn ponem zey gut.

00:11:50.572 --> 00:11:55.809
vem eynem hob ikh gekent oyfn ponem ober zeyer gut hob ikh zey ale gekent, ober az ikh zol zogn nemen,

00:11:56.558 --> 00:12:02.357
a khuts yidn, andere natsyonal- natsyonaln zenen gevezn in in AUSCHWITZ in lager?

00:12:01.452 --> 00:12:07.366
ikh vel aykh zogn, ikh bin nisht gekumen, ikh hob, vu ikh bin nor gekumen, vu ikh bin geshtanen, vu ikh hob nor getun, vu ikh hob gearbet,

00:12:07.415 --> 00:12:12.317
hob ikh keyn andere natsyonalistn nisht gezen, oyser ven s'gevezn a por tsigayners vos m'hot gebrengt,

00:12:12.317 --> 00:12:14.303
hobn zey oykh alts farbrent in zelber nakht.

00:12:15.070 --> 00:12:17.595
un tsigayner hobn mit aykh gearbet tsi neyn?

00:12:15.441 --> 00:12:16.762
tsigayners.

00:12:17.555 --> 00:12:23.580
s'geven eyntslne tsigayners, nisht in bay mit mir gearbet, s'geven eyntslne tsigayners vos hobn yo gearbet oyf andere platsovkes,

00:12:23.580 --> 00:12:30.319
ober ikh zol zogn kristn, iz nisht ge- iz gevezn getseylte oyf di finger, getseylte oyf di finger.

00:12:30.662 --> 00:12:36.056
un ir hot gehert fun homoseksueln vos zenen gebrakht gevorn keyn AUSHCWITZ?

00:12:34.054 --> 00:12:38.520
hob ikh nisht hob ikh nisht gehert, neyn, hob ikh nisht gehert. dos hob ikh nisht gehert.

00:12:38.577 --> 00:12:41.608
dos hob ikh nisht gevust. dos hob ikh nisht gehert.

00:12:42.542 --> 00:12:45.455
un demolts ven m'hot aykh genumen a-

00:12:45.192 --> 00:12:46.249
toytn-marsh.

00:12:45.765 --> 00:12:48.054
a- afn afn toyt MARCH,

00:12:47.487 --> 00:12:48.291
ya.

00:12:48.128 --> 00:12:50.856
di date genoy ven es iz gevezn?

00:12:50.406 --> 00:12:52.189
dos iz geven akhtstn yanuar.

00:12:52.870 --> 00:12:54.180
akhtstn yanuar.

00:12:53.393 --> 00:12:55.530
nayntsn finef un fertsik.

00:12:58.523 --> 00:13:02.685
vi azoy hot zikh es ongehoybn? ir gedenkt genoy vi azoy s'iz geshen?

00:13:00.700 --> 00:13:07.309
yo, s'hot zikh ongehoybn zikher, m'iz gegangen tsu fus, m'hot undz oysgeshtelt tsu fus, un m'hot geheysn eyn zakh nor nemen, nor nemen a koldre oyf zikh.

00:13:07.382 --> 00:13:12.658
undz ze'mir gegangen ir veyst dokh di dos iz geven ir veyst dokh in yanuar vos iz in EUROPE, s'dokh nisht zumer.

00:13:12.681 --> 00:13:16.315
ze'mir gegangen mit di holtserne shikh un di pizhames undzere, di di PASIAK,

00:13:16.315 --> 00:13:22.005
un m'hot nor gezogt eyn zakh, vos ir kent nor nemen kent ir nor nemen, yeder eyner zol zikh nemen a SMICHA, a aza koldre.

00:13:22.063 --> 00:13:23.317
hot men zikh genumen a koldre.

00:13:23.317 --> 00:13:26.766
un m'hot zikh gehaltn fir mentshn di breyt. ir veyst m'iz gegangen tsu fir.

00:13:27.379 --> 00:13:30.101
iz er gegangen gantse teg un gantse nakht.

00:13:30.101 --> 00:13:36.202
bay nakht, geyendik, hot men gemakht a TOR, du yetst shlofstu halbe sho.

00:13:36.202 --> 00:13:37.383
hot men gehaltn bay di hent.

00:13:37.383 --> 00:13:41.329
hot er tsugemakht di oygn. un ge- ober er iz gegangen, shloft, nor tsumakhn di oygn.

00:13:41.571 --> 00:13:44.585
nokh a halbe sho, der anderer zol tsumakhn di oygn.

00:13:44.777 --> 00:13:49.985
nokh a halbe sho, ikh, nakher vayter der bruder. un m'hot zikh azoy gehaltn unter di orems, un azoy hot men gevokt.

00:13:51.308 --> 00:13:56.178
ober vos iz, un tsu morgns iz geven kalt, un ales, keyn esn hot men nisht gegebn,

00:13:56.826 --> 00:13:58.828
un ikh bin durkhgegangen oykh derfer,

00:13:58.935 --> 00:14:03.893
vu ikh hob gezen a mol, un yo, un lebn mir iz gegangen an S.S. man iz er geven an elterer mentsh.

00:14:03.893 --> 00:14:05.640
er hot gehat an OFNAYIM mit zikh.

00:14:05.640 --> 00:14:13.560
oyfn OFNAYIM hot er gehat a ruk-zak, ir veyst dokh, dort in dem ruk-zak hot er gehat esn, vurshtn, veystu farshidene, mit broytn, mit DRINKS,

00:14:15.085 --> 00:14:17.441
un in UNK, er iz oykh gegangen mit undz.

00:14:17.447 --> 00:14:19.618
un m'iz gegangen, m'iz gegangen, m'iz gegangen.

00:14:19.641 --> 00:14:23.735
oyfn veg hob ikh mikh gemakht a shpas tsu im, zog ikh, FATHER,

00:14:24.501 --> 00:14:28.191
LASSEN SIE MICH ⟨oysraysn⟩, ikh zol nor kenen antloyfn.

00:14:29.648 --> 00:14:33.033
zogt er, "makh MAL di SCHNAUZE tsu du yunger!"

00:14:33.259 --> 00:14:34.400
hob ikh geshvign.

00:14:34.845 --> 00:14:42.129
tsvey sho shpeter, zog ikh, FATHER, LASSEN SIE MICH oysraysn. ikh zol antloyfn. LASSEN SIE MICH antloyfn.

00:14:44.228 --> 00:14:45.319
o NO!

00:14:47.147 --> 00:14:50.263
m'iz ongekumen oyf a plats, m'hot gemakht a STOP,

00:14:50.590 --> 00:14:54.246
hot er badorfn geyn er hot badorfn geyn in in TOILET.

00:14:54.893 --> 00:14:57.654
undz hot men gemakht vu m'iz geshtanen. er iz gegangen in TOILET.

00:14:57.677 --> 00:15:00.641
hot er mir ibergegebn dem OFNAYIM, ikh zol haltn.

00:15:01.187 --> 00:15:05.467
vi ikh hob gezen fun der vaytns er geyt arayn in TOILET arayn, hob ikh gegebn a makh oyf gegebn dem zak,

00:15:06.148 --> 00:15:10.681
hot er gehat lign farshidene shtiker broytn dortn, halb broyt, halbe broytn a sakh.

00:15:10.823 --> 00:15:15.857
hob ikh gegebn a khap aroys a halb broyt, ir hert? mit a shtik vursht,

00:15:15.857 --> 00:15:19.422
gegebn dem bruder, un gegebn mir, tsurik tsugemakht dem zak,

00:15:19.480 --> 00:15:23.979
m'hot oyfge- biz er iz tsurikgekumen hot men es oyfgegesn. m'iz gekumen tsu zikh.

00:15:24.137 --> 00:15:27.860
er hot mir gegebn dem zak tsu haltn mitn OFNAYIM. mit dem BICYCLE.

00:15:29.757 --> 00:15:33.699
er kumt tsurik, geyt er esn. er geyt esn, shtey ikh un kuk.

00:15:34.093 --> 00:15:38.948
git er shnayd op nokh a shtikl broyt, zogt er, na dir du yunger! na dir! git er mir shtikl broyt.

00:15:39.122 --> 00:15:40.854
nem ikh a halbs, gib dem bruder.

00:15:41.873 --> 00:15:46.575
un azoy mir hobn zikh opgeshlept zikh biz Gleyvits. m'iz arayngekumen keyn Gleyvits iz geven a yidisher lager.

00:15:46.817 --> 00:15:49.595
hot men undz arayngefirt dort bay nakht, opruen zikh.

00:15:49.348 --> 00:15:50.827
in Gleyvits?

00:15:49.686 --> 00:15:51.429
in Gleyvits.

00:15:51.340 --> 00:15:53.004
vu iz dos a,

00:15:51.429 --> 00:15:55.738
Gleyvits dos tsvishn di grenets fun der tsvishn Poyln un Daytshland.

00:15:56.824 --> 00:15:58.488
un vi shraybt zikh Gleyvits?

00:15:58.478 --> 00:16:03.567
Gleyvitse. Gleyvits. yeder eyner veyst vu Gleyvits.

00:16:03.979 --> 00:16:08.242
dos iz geven oyf der poylisher zayt, oder tsi oyf der daytsher zayt?

00:16:06.747 --> 00:16:09.103
oyf daytsher zayt. Gleyvits.

00:16:09.143 --> 00:16:11.280
un vos a lager iz dos gevezn in Gleyvits?

00:16:10.712 --> 00:16:12.663
s- dortn iz geven a lager fun yidn.

00:16:13.024 --> 00:16:16.865
ober dos iz geve- arbets lager, ober vos iz dortn UNK on iz geven leydik.

00:16:13.429 --> 00:16:14.790
a arbets lager?

00:16:16.956 --> 00:16:19.037
vos iz geven? m'hot undz arayngefirt,

00:16:19.037 --> 00:16:25.117
hob ikh mikh avekgeleygt, gey ikh tsum bruder, zog ikh tsum bruder, du leyg dikh avek, ikh gey aroys gebn a kuk vu iz do do ergets a

00:16:26.102 --> 00:16:28.796
epes tsu khapn epes esn, efsher vel ikh kenen epes trefn.

00:16:29.106 --> 00:16:32.289
gey ikh vu zukht men? in der kekh. ikh zukh di kekh.

00:16:32.650 --> 00:16:37.200
gey ikh tsu s'geven niderike hayzer, ikh geb a makh oyf di lodn, ze ikh s'ofn.

00:16:37.678 --> 00:16:44.087
ikh gey arayn ineveynik arayn, tref ikh di gantse kesl, a UNK fule kesl, di groyse kesl, UNK kartofl, opgekokhte kartofl.

00:16:44.087 --> 00:16:46.110
ikh nem a kartofl, veykh vi gold.

00:16:46.369 --> 00:16:49.265
ikh hoyb on tsu esn. nem ikh arop dos hitl un ful op a ful hitl,

00:16:49.980 --> 00:16:56.859
un ikh breng arayn dos tsu mayn bruder tsum oyfn oyfn bet. zogt er, reboyne-shel-oylem. es, zogt er, vifl du vilst. ikh gey tsurik brengen nokh.

00:16:56.950 --> 00:16:58.986
ikh bin tsurikgekumen iz shoyn gevezn dortn ful.

00:16:59.177 --> 00:17:05.229
ikh bin arayngegangen, hob ikh gekhapt nokh, ongekumen di S.S., m'hot geshrign HERAUS!

00:17:05.387 --> 00:17:08.047
un ver s'aroysgelofn hot men derlangt a shtekn ibern kop,

00:17:09.369 --> 00:17:16.501
un ikh vayter, ikh hob ongeleygt zikh ful mit nokh mit POTATOES, un ikh bin aroysgeshprungen fun fentster, hobn nisht espiet mir tsu gebn a klap

00:17:16.693 --> 00:17:19.572
un ikh bin gelofn arayn tsum bruder, nokh mit ful mit kartofl.

00:17:19.950 --> 00:17:22.661
un m'hot dos mit zikh gehaltn, un m'iz gegangen vayter.

00:17:23.241 --> 00:17:28.010
biz azoy lang gegang- gegangen biz m'iz gegangen dentsmol du veyst dokh iber iber Tshekhoslovakye.

00:17:29.637 --> 00:17:35.857
in Tshekhoslovakye, dos hot dos dertseyl ikh nor, dos dos hot nisht genumen biz azoy haynt un morgn, m'iz gegangen azoy gantse vokhn.

00:17:36.049 --> 00:17:37.865
m'iz adurkhgegangen nokh Tshekhoslovakye,

00:17:39.120 --> 00:17:44.497
oy, hobn zey shoyn gevust di tshekhn az do kumen zey on mater- az do kumen zey op a transport vos zey geyen tsu fus oyfn toytn-marsh.

00:17:44.672 --> 00:17:47.619
hot men gehaltn broyt mit vaser. un undz hot men geshrign, broyt!

00:17:47.630 --> 00:17:51.939
vaser! broyt! vaser! di gevald undz zenen gevezn. zey hobn gevorfn broyt,

00:17:51.939 --> 00:17:54.151
dos iz geven goyim, mit vaser.

00:17:54.004 --> 00:17:54.993
di tshekhn?

00:17:54.645 --> 00:17:55.736
di tshekhn.

00:17:55.978 --> 00:18:01.439
hobn di S.S. genumen shisn un zenen antlofn. ver s'hot gekhapt, der hot gekhapt. ver s'hot nisht gekhapt zenen antlofn.

00:18:02.847 --> 00:18:08.058
un shoyn. mit eyn mol geyt men nokh nokh a dorf. m'iz adurkhgegangen nokh a dorf, nokh a dorf adurkhgegangen. ir hert?

00:18:08.058 --> 00:18:11.464
shteyt a goy, ze ikh fun der vaytns, hert?

00:18:11.554 --> 00:18:17.842
er varft dortn kartofl un kokht di kartofl un er shit aroyf leym, far di khazeyrim.

00:18:19.283 --> 00:18:21.319
gib ikh a loyf aroys fun der shure,

00:18:21.561 --> 00:18:28.406
un gib a khap tsvey fule hent, leym mit di kartofl, un loyf arayn tsurik. un der S.S. man zet mir zogt er, du!

00:18:29.337 --> 00:18:31.123
hunt hunt! ikh bin shoyn tsurik do.

00:18:31.197 --> 00:18:37.417
un gebn dem bruder, es. genumen esn. mitn leym, mit alem, s'gold.

00:18:37.643 --> 00:18:40.640
ikh gegesn, er hot gegesn, vayter derkhapt dos harts.

00:18:41.912 --> 00:18:46.040
un azoy a mol hot men zikh opgedreyt zikh bizkale merts.

00:18:46.333 --> 00:18:48.605
februar, ende februar. merts.

00:18:49.202 --> 00:18:55.963
m'iz shoyn arayngekumen keyn Daytshland. m'iz shoyn geven in Daytshland. hot men undz gefirt mit vagonen ahin un tsurik biz m'hot undz gefirt arayn nakher keyn Dakhau.

00:18:56.458 --> 00:19:00.434
un a khuts di vagonen hot men hot ir gegangen tsu fus ale mol?

00:19:00.070 --> 00:19:05.644
in Doytshland ze'mir shoyn gegangen mit di vagonen. biz tsu der Doytshland, bizn Doytshland, tsu fus.

00:19:03.090 --> 00:19:05.294
biz Doytshland zent ir gegangen tsu fus?

00:19:05.644 --> 00:19:11.286
vifl ze'mir ongekumen. ze'mir aroysgegangen dortn aza iz aroysgegangen efsher tsvey toyznt iz men gegangen,un m'iz ongekumen tsvey dray hundert.

00:19:12.068 --> 00:19:13.361
s'hot UNK.

00:19:12.135 --> 00:19:13.850
vos iz geshen tsu der reshte?

00:19:13.502 --> 00:19:19.503
zey hobn zikh avekgezetst, zey hobn gegesn ayz, zey hobn gegesn shney, hobn gekrign hobn gekrign a UNK, avekgezetst hot men zey tsu geshosn.

00:19:19.695 --> 00:19:24.816
m'hot gegebn a bafel nakher di di soltisn oyf di oyf di vegn m'zol arop roymen di toyte.

00:19:24.977 --> 00:19:28.653
vayl di shlitenes kenen nisht forn, di toyte lign oyf di gasn, oyf der HIGHWAY.

00:19:28.791 --> 00:19:32.868
hot men gegebn a bafel tsu yeder soltis zol aroysshikn di mentshn zol arop roymen di toyte.

00:19:32.740 --> 00:19:34.371
un ale zenen gevezn yidn?

00:19:34.242 --> 00:19:35.552
alts iz geven yidn.

00:19:35.760 --> 00:19:38.066
un di vekhters ver zenen gevezn, daytshn?

00:19:37.836 --> 00:19:39.872
he? di vekhters, daytshn.

00:19:40.367 --> 00:19:41.688
nisht keyn andere

00:19:40.384 --> 00:19:41.475
ver s'hot es,

00:19:41.667 --> 00:19:44.664
keyn andere nisht, nisht keyn ukrainer, nor daytshn.

00:19:41.688 --> 00:19:42.740
natsyonaln?

00:19:44.991 --> 00:19:45.975
S.S.

00:19:45.975 --> 00:19:50.236
un ver s'hot zikh avekgezetst, er hot zikh ni- er hot zikh nisht bald nisht gekent unterheybn zikh, zogt er,

00:19:50.236 --> 00:19:53.928
hot er genumen dos biksl un derlangt a koyl. geblibn zitsn.

00:19:54.036 --> 00:19:56.224
un ven hot zikh der MARCH geendikt?

00:19:56.483 --> 00:20:00.071
der marsh hot zikh geendikt ven m'iz aroyfgegangen oyf di vagones un m'hot undz arayngefirt keyn Dakho.

00:20:00.921 --> 00:20:02.467
in lager in Dakhau?

00:20:02.052 --> 00:20:02.873
ya.

00:20:03.115 --> 00:20:05.049
arayngefirt keyn Dakho in lager,

00:20:03.823 --> 00:20:05.926
vos a date iz dos gevezn gedenkt ir?

00:20:06.895 --> 00:20:12.221
dos iz gevezn in di BEGINNING OF OF merts, ende ende februar merts.

00:20:13.054 --> 00:20:18.262
iz hot men geven in Dakhau, un gearbet dort oykh epes a a dray vokhn, biz ende merts,

00:20:19.652 --> 00:20:22.312
un nakher hot men gegangen, biz ende merts

00:20:23.010 --> 00:20:27.239
hot men dortn gearbet farshidene arbetn. nakher hot men gegangen m'hot undz vider aroysgefirt,

00:20:27.415 --> 00:20:30.170
fun Dakho. fun Dakho.

00:20:27.921 --> 00:20:29.299
fun D- fun Dakhau?

00:20:30.170 --> 00:20:34.479
un m'hot undz aroysgefirt oykhet aroys oyf di vegn, tsurik oyf di vagonen.

00:20:34.772 --> 00:20:37.820
tsurik ongelodnt di vagonen. vu fort men yetst? m'veyst nisht.

00:20:38.788 --> 00:20:44.013
ongelodnt di vagonen, farshlosn di vagonen, ir hert? un m'firt undz.

00:20:44.087 --> 00:20:51.084
dort men ahin, m'fort tsurik. m'fort ahin, un m'fort tsurik. teg un nakht.

00:20:51.681 --> 00:20:54.037
m'varft undz arayn a shtikl broyt a tog,

00:20:53.841 --> 00:20:55.573
vifl zent ir geven in a vagon?

00:20:55.528 --> 00:21:00.736
in di vagonen? efsher hot gekont zayn dentsmolt efsher a finef hundert mentshn.

00:21:01.333 --> 00:21:03.571
ober in eyn vagon vifl flegt arayngeyn?

00:21:04.067 --> 00:21:09.360
s'arayngegangen az m'hot nisht gehat keyn otem. m'hot nisht gekont UNK.

00:21:10.935 --> 00:21:19.907
un ikh hob nokh gehat a tsvey kartofl in mayn tash vos ikh hob es nisht gerirt, roye. ir hert? roye kartofl in der tash.

00:21:20.655 --> 00:21:25.610
un az m'fort in di vagonen, m'git nisht keyn broyt, un m'git gornisht, mayn bruder farkhalesht zikh,

00:21:25.650 --> 00:21:31.769
hot men ayngeribn mit a shtikl kartofl hot men im gegebn, un do dortn, ayngeribn di shleyfn. halt dikh.

00:21:33.312 --> 00:21:37.963
un Got mit eyn mol gibn di S.S. a for avek,

00:21:38.037 --> 00:21:44.004
un m'lozt undz iber fray, un m'freyt zikh, mir zenen bafrayt gevorn. di S.S. zenen antlofn.

00:21:44.618 --> 00:21:47.109
m'hot gevust az di un di krig di krig geyt tsu ende.

00:21:48.465 --> 00:21:58.027
un m'shteyt zikh un m'freyt zikh un m'freyt zikh. mit eyn mol nokh a sho tsayt get a kum op a tsveyte vagon oyf der tsveyter zayt un UNK geyen aroys S.S. azoy vi in a front arayn.

00:21:58.303 --> 00:22:05.570
HELMETS, mit hant-granatn, mit mashin-gever, m- ayngeshtekt hant-granatn, vey iz mir nebekh, in a front arayn.

00:22:05.644 --> 00:22:13.164
un m'shrayt, JUDEN RAUS! HUNDE RAUS! un m'heybt on oyftsushlisn di vagonen, m'shlist oyf di vagonen, RAUS!

00:22:14.723 --> 00:22:23.604
un m'hoybt undz op aroystsushikn, un ikh zog tsum bruder, un bay yeder aroysgeyn get men a shtekn oyfn kop. on dem heybt zikh dokh nisht on. a shtekn oyfn kop, yeder eyner vos geyt aroys fun vagon.

00:22:23.604 --> 00:22:30.866
ikh zog tsum bruder, du zolst gebn a shpring arop, zolst nisht khapn keyn shtekn, vayl tomer khapstu a shtekn bistu shoyn farloyrn. du darfst nisht mer nor a klap.

00:22:31.193 --> 00:22:32.722
eyn klap bistu fertik.

00:22:33.437 --> 00:22:40.147
zogt er, vi makht men dos? du vest es muzn makhn. gib dikh a sh- varf aroys, du zolst flien. az du vest nisht khapn keyn shtekn vestu dikh oyfheybn.

00:22:40.879 --> 00:22:46.054
un azoy iz gevezn. ikh hob im gegebn kuk vi er flit aroys, er hot nisht gekhapt keyn shtekn, Got tsu dank.

00:22:46.279 --> 00:22:51.994
ikh bin gefloygn vayter. geven yung, gegebn a shprung aroys. vi hot er aza lange shtekn tsu mir?

00:22:52.388 --> 00:22:54.317
ver s'hot gekhapt hot gekhapt, ver s'hot nisht gekhapt,

00:22:54.317 --> 00:22:58.727
un m'hot undz gefirt durkh di felder glaykh arayn in vald arayn.

00:22:59.526 --> 00:23:04.532
zog ikh tsum bruder, dos iz undzer letster veg. dos iz es.

00:23:04.842 --> 00:23:09.865
m'shlept undz arayn in vald oystsushisn. nor gedenk eyn zakh zog ikh tsun im, in geyn,

00:23:10.022 --> 00:23:12.395
m'kumt arayn in vald arayn, mir veln beyde antloyfn.

00:23:13.279 --> 00:23:17.273
azoy vi m'derzet di beymer, azoy heybn mir on tsu loyfn.

00:23:17.616 --> 00:23:21.120
un dos iz gevezn. m'iz arayngekumen in vald arayn, m'hot ongehoybn tsu loyfn,

00:23:21.767 --> 00:23:31.498
loyfn undz nokh tsvey S.S., "ir HUNDE shteyn blaybn!" m'shist, "shteyn blaybn!" m'shist. un ikh zog tsum bruder, kuk dikh nisht um un loyf!

00:23:31.656 --> 00:23:33.118
ikh bin gelofn unter im.

00:23:34.558 --> 00:23:43.870
un m'loyft un m'loyft, undz ze'mir gelofn efsher a sho. un di tsvey kholeres lo- geyn lozn zikh nisht op. un m'loyft nokh undz, un m'shrayt, HUNDE shteyn blaybn!

00:23:43.870 --> 00:23:51.360
un mir loyfn, zey loyfn. un der bruder Avram khapt a koyl in kop arayn, un falt arop,

00:23:51.552 --> 00:23:55.629
un ikh shray, Avrom! Avrom! ikh hob shoyn nisht vemen tsu redn.

00:23:56.023 --> 00:24:01.012
un nokh dem geb ikh a kuk, di tsvey S.S. dernentern zikh tsu mir. bin ikh oyfgehoybn un antlofn.

00:24:02.082 --> 00:24:07.982
ikh bin antlofn, hobn zey mikh shoyn nisht nokhgeyogt. zey hobn shoyn gezen er iz shoyn toyt, hobn zikh getrakht zikh, loyf.

00:24:08.528 --> 00:24:13.584
un ikh bin gelofn a gantsn tog biz shpet fintster in der nakht in di velder.

00:24:15.379 --> 00:24:19.726
ikh hob nisht gornisht gezen nor loyfn. ikh hob afile nisht gevolt umkukn zikh.

00:24:19.935 --> 00:24:24.024
un dan nakher bin ikh antshlofn gevorn. ikh hob zikh aropgezetst antshlofn gevorn,

00:24:24.024 --> 00:24:28.738
oyfgevekt fir in der fri, in der fri, s'hot ongehoybn tsu togn,

00:24:29.706 --> 00:24:36.028
un ikh shtey un veyn, reboyne-shel-oylem, vos hostu mit mir gemakht? ikh hob gehat eyn bruder, host mikh shoyn avekgeharget oykhet.

00:24:36.143 --> 00:24:41.200
vos hostu mit mir gemakht? vi nemt men yetst esn? vi geyt men aroys fun vald aroys?

00:24:41.451 --> 00:24:45.445
vu gey ikh? a gantser tog bin ikh gelofn in vald on an ek.

00:24:46.935 --> 00:24:53.983
hob ikh genumen raysn groz. ikh hob gerisn groz, ikh zol hobn dem kvas, dem dos, dem di a bisl epes in moyl aroys.

00:24:55.474 --> 00:24:56.885
un ikh hoyb on tsu geyn.

00:24:56.993 --> 00:25:03.686
ikh hoyb on tsu geyn, bin ikh gegangen efsher tsen fuftsn minut, geb ikh a derze a hoyz un nokh a hoyz, oy iz dos a derfl. ikh gey arayn.

00:25:04.165 --> 00:25:09.741
zol shoyn dortn zayn Hitler, zol zayn Himler, ver s'zol nisht zayn. ikh gey arayn, ikh geb zikh unter, ikh ken nisht mer.

00:25:09.741 --> 00:25:14.446
un der toyt ligt in di oygn, ikh ken nisht mer, ikh ken nisht mer kemfn. ikh gib zikh unter.

00:25:14.627 --> 00:25:16.595
un bin arayn in dem hoyz arayn,

00:25:18.222 --> 00:25:25.016
un ikh red tsu der froy, ikh klap on bay der tir, zog ikh, "ken ICH bite EINE CAFE HABBEN? ikh hob nisht gevolt nemen keyn broyt, efsher hobn zey oykh nisht tsulib der milkhome.

00:25:25.022 --> 00:25:32.528
kukt zi mikh on, ikh red tsu zi a nayes daytsh un EVERYTHING un zi hot moyre gehat far mir, ikh ikh hob oysgezen punkt vi a payats mit aza hitl, mit

00:25:32.528 --> 00:25:34.567
holtserne shikh mit aza PASIAK.

00:25:34.573 --> 00:25:40.054
ruft zi dem man, der man get a kum tsu, JA WAS WUNSCHEN SIE? zog ikh zog ikh, koydem kol zog ikh, gris Got, gris Got.

00:25:40.054 --> 00:25:44.389
un ikh hob mikh mit im tseredt, un un un ikh dertseyl im dos ales.

00:25:46.757 --> 00:25:56.352
un er veyst er, er hot mikh oyfgeheybn, un er makht mir kave. un er zogt mir, kum arayn bite, ikh zol arayngeyn mit ineveynik.

00:25:56.967 --> 00:26:08.031
kum arayn, zets zikh avek barn tish, un er gibt mir kave. un brengt arayn azoy vi a halber tish. un ikh ze dos broyt,

00:26:08.408 --> 00:26:10.581
un zey hobn gehat dortn a tokhter oyfgevekt,

00:26:10.581 --> 00:26:14.595
hobn zey geshnitn gantse reftlekh un ongeshmirt mit der mit mit marmelad.

00:26:14.719 --> 00:26:18.594
un vi lang er shmirt dray reftlekh, hob ikh shoyn arayngelozt. aza,

00:26:17.638 --> 00:26:19.674
er hot gevust az ir zent a yid?

00:26:19.579 --> 00:26:20.383
he?

00:26:20.001 --> 00:26:21.783
er hot gevust az ir zent a yid?

00:26:20.642 --> 00:26:25.845
no no. er hot mikh gefregt ver ikh bin. zog ikh, ICH bin, zog ikh, EIN POLE. zogt er, SIE SPRECHEN dokh SO SO UNK.

00:26:25.885 --> 00:26:30.955
SO NICE doytsh. zog ikh, ICH bin a P- a POLE, heyst a goy. ikh bin a po- ikh bin nisht keyn yid. ikh hob nisht gezogt ikh bin a yid.

00:26:31.729 --> 00:26:34.912
ANYWAYS, hin un aher, ikh hoyb on tsu esn un tsu trinken,

00:26:35.661 --> 00:26:41.173
un dos iz es. un er shrayt tsu mir, nakher fregt zi mikh, di froy, vi azoy HABEN SIE SO hunger?

00:26:41.533 --> 00:26:44.027
hob ikh gezogt, ikh kum fun Oyshvits, fun di lagern,

00:26:44.027 --> 00:26:47.681
o! mayn Got! UNK DARUM HABEN SIE SO hunger!

00:26:47.681 --> 00:26:53.950
hin aher, zog ikh, "ICH vil ZICH dos dos badanken, ikh hob UNK, keyn gelt. viln SIE mayn MUTZE HABBEN?

00:26:54.558 --> 00:27:01.541
viln SIE mayne shikh HABBEN?" "neyn. vu WOLLEN SIE den geyn?" "ikh vil geyn zukhn di COMPANY, di khevre."

00:27:02.928 --> 00:27:06.843
zi hot gevust vos tut zikh. zogt zi tsu mir, di fir, geyen SIE bite nisht RAUS,

00:27:06.843 --> 00:27:10.604
zi hot shoyn moyre gehat di shkheynim zoln mikh nisht zen. az di shkheynim veln mikh hobn gezen,

00:27:10.604 --> 00:27:12.491
ebn zey fornemen tsu di zhandamerye, far vos hot

00:27:12.493 --> 00:27:16.222
gehaltn do a yid. zi hot im gelozt aroysgeyn. far vos zey hobn nisht gefodert far di POLICE.

00:27:15.469 --> 00:27:17.387
zi hot shoyn ye gevust az ir zent a yid?

00:27:17.140 --> 00:27:22.669
